}}'''''The Runes of Zendos''''' is a 1984 video game published by [[Dorcas Software]]. It is the sequel to ''The Oracle's Cave''.

==Gameplay==
''The Runes of Zendos'' is a game in which the merry principality of Dorcasia is conquered by the evil [[Magician (fantasy)|wizard]] of Zendos, and the player must rescue the twelve months that the wizard has trapped in a hidden hourglass.<ref name="Imagine24"/>

